{
  "nbformat": 4,
  "nbformat_minor": 5,
  "metadata": {
    "kernelspec": {
      "name": "maxima",
      "display_name": "Maxima",
      "language": "maxima"
    },
    "aximar": {}
  },
  "cells": [
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "# Vector Fields and Streamlines\n\nDerive vector fields from symbolic potentials and visualize them with `ax_vector_field` and `ax_streamline`.\n\nThis notebook highlights the **symbolic-numeric bridge**: we use Maxima's symbolic differentiation to compute gradient fields from scalar potentials, then feed those expressions directly to ax-plots for numerical sampling and rendering.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "load(\"numerics\")$\nload(\"ax-plots\")$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 89,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## Gradient Fields from a Scalar Potential\n\nGiven a scalar potential $V(x,y)$, the associated conservative field is $\\mathbf{F} = -\\nabla V$.\n\nWe start with the simplest case: a quadratic potential well $V = x^2 + y^2$, whose gradient field points radially inward.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Define scalar potential and compute gradient symbolically */\nV : x^2 + y^2$\nFx : -diff(V, x)$\nFy : -diff(V, y)$\nprint(\"F =\", [Fx, Fy])$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 90,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "F = [-(2*x),-(2*y)]"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Visualize the gradient field — arrows point toward the origin */\nax_draw2d(\n  ngrid=12,\n  ax_vector_field(Fx, Fy, x, -3, 3, y, -3, 3),\n  title=\"Gradient of V = x^2 + y^2\",\n  aspect_ratio=true\n)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 91,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "data": {
            "application/x-maxima-plotly": [
              "{\"data\":[{\"x\":[-3.0,-2.691444313664052,null,-3.0,-2.691444313664052,null,-3.0,-2.691444313664052,null,-3.0,-2.691444313664052,null,-3.0,-2.691444313664052,null,-3.0,-2.691444313664052,null,-3.0,-2.691444313664052,null,-3.0,-2.691444313664052,null,-3.0,-2.691444313664052,null,-3.0,-2.691444313664052,null,-3.0,-2.691444313664052,null,-3.0,-2.691444313664052,null,-2.4545454545454546,-2.2020908020887697,null,-2.4545454545454546,-2.2020908020887697,null,-2.4545454545454546,-2.2020908020887697,null,-2.4545454545454546,-2.2020908020887697,null,-2.4545454545454546,-2.2020908020887697,null,-2.4545454545454546,-2.2020908020887697,null,-2.4545454545454546,-2.2020908020887697,null,-2.4545454545454546,-2.2020908020887697,null,-2.4545454545454546,-2.2020908020887697,null,-2.4545454545454546,-2.2020908020887697,null,-2.4545454545454546,-2.2020908020887697,null,-2.4545454545454546,-2.2020908020887697,null,-1.9090909090909092,-1.7127372905134877,null,-1.9090909090909092,-1.7127372905134877,null,-1.9090909090909092,-1.7127372905134877,null,-1.9090909090909092,-1.7127372905134877,null,-1.9090909090909092,-1.7127372905134877,null,-1.9090909090909092,-1.7127372905134877,null,-1.9090909090909092,-1.7127372905134877,null,-1.9090909090909092,-1.7127372905134877,null,-1.9090909090909092,-1.7127372905134877,null,-1.9090909090909092,-1.7127372905134877,null,-1.9090909090909092,-1.7127372905134877,null,-1.9090909090909092,-1.7127372905134877,null,-1.3636363636363638,-1.2233837789382056,null,-1.3636363636363638,-1.2233837789382056,null,-1.3636363636363638,-1.2233837789382056,null,-1.3636363636363638,-1.2233837789382056,null,-1.3636363636363638,-1.2233837789382056,null,-1.3636363636363638,-1.2233837789382056,null,-1.3636363636363638,-1.2233837789382056,null,-1.3636363636363638,-1.2233837789382056,null,-1.3636363636363638,-1.2233837789382056,null,-1.3636363636363638,-1.2233837789382056,null,-1.3636363636363638,-1.2233837789382056,null,-1.3636363636363638,-1.2233837789382056,nul