    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## Fluid Flow: Rotational Field\n\nThe field $\\mathbf{F} = (-y, x)$ describes rigid-body rotation. The vector field and streamlines together form a classic phase portrait.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
