    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## Source and Sink Flow\n\nA radial source field $\\mathbf{F} = \\frac{(x, y)}{x^2+y^2+\\epsilon}$ points outward from the origin. Streamlines radiate outward like spokes.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Source flow: vector field + streamlines */\nSx : x/(x^2 + y^2 + 0.1)$\nSy : y/(x^2 + y^2 + 0.1)$\n\nax_draw2d(\n  color=\"#cccccc\", name=\"F\", ngrid=12, ax_vector_field(Sx, Sy, x, -3, 3, y, -3, 3),\n  color=\"blue\", name=\"streamline\", ax_streamline(Sx, Sy, x, -3, 3, y, -3, 3),\n  aspect_ratio=true, title=\"Source Flow\"\n)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 97,
      "outputs": [
        {
