          "metadata": {},
          "output_type": "display_data"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## Curl and Divergence Analysis\n\nFor a 2D vector field $\\mathbf{F} = (P(x,y),\\; Q(x,y))$:\n\n- **Divergence:** $\\nabla \\cdot \\mathbf{F} = \\frac{\\partial P}{\\partial x} + \\frac{\\partial Q}{\\partial y}$ (measures local expansion/compression)\n- **Curl (scalar in 2D):** $(\\nabla \\times \\mathbf{F})_z = \\frac{\\partial Q}{\\partial x} - \\frac{\\partial P}{\\partial y}$ (measures local rotation)\n\nWe apply these to our rotational and source flows, computing everything symbolically.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Define divergence and curl for 2D fields */\ndiv2d(P, Q) := diff(P, x) + diff(Q, y)$\ncurl2d(P, Q) := diff(Q, x) - diff(P, y)$\n\n/* Rotational flow: F = (-y, x) */\nprint(\"=== Rotational flow F = (-y, x) ===\")$\nprint(\"div  =\", div2d(-y, x))$\nprint(\"curl =\", curl2d(-y, x))$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 98,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "=== Rotational flow F = (-y, x) ===\ndiv  = 0\ncurl = 2"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Source flow: F = (x, y)/(x^2+y^2+0.1) */\nprint(\"=== Source flow ===\")$\ndiv_source : ratsimp(div2d(Sx, Sy))$\ncurl_source : ratsimp(curl2d(Sx, Sy))$\nprint(\"div  =\", div_source)$\nprint(\"curl =\", curl_source)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 99,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "=== Source flow ===\nrat: replaced 0.1 by 1/10 = 0.1\nrat: replaced 0.1 by 1/10 = 0.1\nrat: replaced 0.1 by 1/10 = 0.1\ndiv  = 20/(100*y^4+(200*x^2+20)*y^2+100*x^4+20*x^2+1)\ncurl = 0"
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}